# Reserved for shared Lua helpers used by envoy's `envoy.filters.http.lua`
# in p02-jwt (jwt_hs256.lua), p08-req-body / p09-resp-body
# (body_rewrite.lua), and p10-full-pipeline. Envoy's Lua runtime differs
# from OpenResty's, so these helpers are *not* the same files the nginx
# column uses — they live in their own directory.
#
# This .gitkeep is only here so the directory is present before the
# first helper lands. Every profile's `docker-compose.yaml` mounts
# this directory at /etc/envoy/lualib read-only; profiles that do not
# need a Lua helper simply never reference the mount.
